到更好的維護。<br />\n<br />\n駱惠寧認為，要在香港社會特別是公職人員和青少年中，加強憲法和基本法教育、國家安全和國情教育、中國歷史和文化教育，讓大家明白樹高千呎有根，水流萬里有源，作為中國人愛國不是一種選擇，而是一種義務，更是一種正道，要更有力築牢愛國愛港的社會政治基礎，增強國家認同感、歸屬感、民族自豪感，香港才能把準前進方向，市民的個人價值才能更好實現。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T03:58:52.000Z","msg":"同一段野講咗幾多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c17152409d48ab7c03a5232b30ef60194b2177f5","tid":2223604,"uid":50386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2997824186af7e66c3bf1d744e0b59056f6f3310","tid":2223604,"uid":126782,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T03:47:28.000Z","msg":"咁事實的確係嚇走左大部分人<br />\n<br />\n街頭已經無人敢出"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T03:59:07.000Z","msg":"解決提出問題嘅人=解決咗問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af2417643b1d00ab461d6da8164e146067a35ec7","tid":2223604,"uid":211466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T03:59:48.000Z","msg":"每日睇住依d 撚屌講埋依D 野, 就好冇癮點解會生存係依個地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f5d3cdb6a6e97d5699eef11074dce7025a1a75","tid":2223604,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9382550039c336a0d66123920591134785144712","tid":2223604,"uid":33370,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T03:20:03.000Z","msg":"想睇中式肉醬意粉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:00:03.000Z","msg":"螞蟻上樹"},{"pid":"59bc0db52cf4b7b77e3152847a89955ef661ab20","tid":2223604,"uid":307398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:00:30.000Z","msg":"乜成語嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c069984f2b18b9c048da0d3a0153bbb9a3181ddb","tid":2223604,"uid":168406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:03:15.000Z","msg":"依家港股升咗27xxx未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj